<div class="services-content">
    <h2 class="section-title">Nuestros Servicios</h2>
    <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
            <div class="service-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Análisis Legal</h3>
            <p>Evaluamos tu caso desde una perspectiva legal y financiera para determinar la mejor estrategia.</p>
            <div class="service-card-footer">
                <span class="service-card-link">Saber más</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
            <div class="service-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Representación Judicial</h3>
            <p>Te representamos en todas las instancias legales necesarias para resolver tu caso.</p>
            <div class="service-card-footer">
                <span class="service-card-link">Saber más</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <div class="service-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-headset"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Asesoría Continua</h3>
            <p>Te acompañamos durante todo el proceso, manteniéndote informado en cada etapa.</p>
            <div class="service-card-footer">
                <span class="service-card-link">Saber más</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .section-title {
        color: var(--color-red);
        margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        position: relative;
        display: inline-block;
        width: 100%;
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .section-title::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 80px;
        height: 4px;
        background-color: var(--color-red);
        border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .services-content {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .services-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .service-card {
        background: var(--color-white);
        border: 1px solid var(--color-gray);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 2rem;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .service-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    
    .service-icon {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .service-icon i {
        font-size: 3rem;
        color: var(--color-red);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .service-card:hover .service-icon i {
        transform: scale(1.1);
        color: var(--color-red-bright);
    }
</style>
